      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing though. even if there are people who might care, it feels like such a heavy burden to carry. like, why bother trying to be seen when it's just going to be exhausting and lonely anyway? sometimes it feels like the only way to actually find some peace is to just... not be a part of it anymore. like just opting out of the whole thing.",
