    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like a way to avoid it, though. it feels more like... finally stopping the noise. everything is just so constant and loud and heavy. if i just wasn't here, the noise would stop. wouldn't it be better for everyone if there was just one less person struggling to stay afloat in a place they don't belong?",
